Creating Line and Stacked Column Chart 15

Creating Line and Stacked Column Chart for Violation Per Month by Race ,Gender, YOY and Out of State Violation

Steps

Violation Per Month by Race, Gender, YOY and Out of State Violation

  1.        Open Visualization Pane
  2.        Select   Line and Stacked Column Chart 
  3.        Drag the visual on to the dashboard
  4.        Drag Race filed from Traffic Violation table to Shared Axis, Gender Field to Column series, Violation Per Month Measure to Column Values, YOY and %Out of State Measure to Line values 

                                                



Download the formatting for the above visual by clicking the red icon
